headline: Newly Launched Deloitte and Palantir Strategic Alliance Delivering Tangible Outcomes, Accelerating Transformation for Clients' Modern Enterprise Functions
summary: In today's rapidly evolving environment, where AI-enterprise scaling is essential for organizations to transform and meet mission-critical objectives more quickly and decisively, Deloitte and Palantir's recently launched strategic alliance is unlocking effective outcomes for government and commercial clients. Together, Deloitte and Palantir have developed an Enterprise Operating System (EOS) combining Deloitte's IP and domain experience with Palantir's Foundry and AIP platforms.
